Source: slots-boot
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Elandig <elan@sestudio.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cargo, rustc
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/Elandig/initramfs-slots-boot

Package: slots-boot
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, initramfs-tools
Description: slot machine that gates your boot until you hit the jackpot
 slots-boot runs from the initramfs and won't let the boot finish until you spin
 7-7-7 on the reels.
 .
 It's a novelty boot gate. Type the recovery word (see the README) at the slot
 screen if you ever need to skip it.
